Source: opengl
Version: 0.0-7
Description: Open Graphics Library (OpenGL) is a cross-language, cross-platform application programming interface (API) for rendering 2D and 3D vector graphics.
Default-Features: impl-select

Feature: impl-select
Description: Feature to select the implementation via build depends since features do not support platform dependent flags
Build-Depends: opengl[core,windows] (windows), opengl[core,mesa] (!windows)

Feature: windows
Description: Use and install OpenGL from WindowsSDK

Feature: mesa
Description: Use and install OpenGL from mesa
Build-Depends: mesa[core]